# Kalli Alran

Affiliation: Ikar's Salvage
Description: Female. Kalli is a brown-skinned Cyran human in her forties who was visiting Sharn on the Day of Mourning. She has a friendly personality and has made it a personal mission to recover artifacts from her homeland.
Location: Sanctuary, Talenta Plains
Mannerisms: Always smiling :)
Motivation: Loyalty
Quote / Flavor: “No one lives forever, eh?”
Race: Human
Role: Quest giver, Scavenger
Status: Alive